cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about image super-resolution using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel method for utilizing recursive architecture, which involves training a neural network to learn from its own output. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, since the paper deals with image processing, it may also belong to the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
